score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T06:00:58.000Z","msg":"梗係唔準<br />\nDQ曬選都無得選丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085e7710e6f847e809c5c274a2fe7058416b6cab","tid":959664,"uid":23400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"其實啱一半，本土派都係贏好少，反而自稱中國人既泛民都係不停贏。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民仲有個特異功能，臨選舉前會去連登洗版，贏唔到就屌票屌足成個禮拜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f45d186f4e3727777a68693a89b5c3c6200b6867","tid":959664,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"真正嘅旁觀者清<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d824e7bfd52923102352f4585acdae7f6ddb31","tid":959664,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"「hate Hong Kong, love China!」<br />\n「love China! Must love!!」<br />\n<img src=\"http://dadazim.com/journal/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/27aa1p4-590x41311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdadazim.com%2Fjournal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F01%2F27aa1p4-590x41311.jpg&h=854022bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e1e18d66acd8d1e8aca00b6e1b64dd7c64b7d97","tid":959664,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T06:41:24.000Z","msg":"所以李光耀可以成為統治者真係有原因<br />\n比起正常人睇野早十成十幾廿年"},{"pid":"49d77f5fc394f5951bf48892dd622d9d30a696f8","tid":959664,"uid":106026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"新加坡要贏就要親支.<br />\n<br />\n用簡體字,講華語運動,培訓支共幹部<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc18ede710b1b0b035af1fd929fd70a5814e290d","tid":959664,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl